from  schools  and  universities.  It  is  more  of  a  research  bill  that  it
is  an  energy  bill,  but  it  pays  for  itself  in  known  quantities  of  en-
ergy  that  are  there.  We  just  can’t  get  them  up,  but  we  are  going
